Re: Quick 2級 question
by Hyperworm » Sat 09.04.2010 10:01 am I'd equate it to "is (generally) held to be ...", or sometimes "is treated as".
fun translation snippets | need something translated?BTC@1KMZXgoWiDshQis5Z7feCx8jaiP4QAB2ks
